<p style="text-align: center;" class="syro-h1"><strong>Original stone carving stone on St. Thomas Mount, Chennai, India. </strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;" class="syro-h1"><strong>(Ca. 650 AD. Feast December 18)</strong></p>


